org.javers.repository.api

Class QueryParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javers.repository.api.QueryParams

  • public class QueryParams
extends java.lang.Object
    Container for additional query parameters used for filtering Snapshots to be fetched from database.
    Query parameters can't affect query semantic as they are used by all types of queries.
    See Also:
    QueryParamsBuilder
